{"tid":492951,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Nvme vs Sata III","createTime":"2017-12-08T04:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T06:10:45.000Z","uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33602d4d448fe1ac90bd98be4bafbb873aa66c17","tid":492951,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"小弟襯黑五大減價，換走左部老爺VAIO。取而代之既係Dell XPS 13 8gb 128g。<br />\n<br />\n本身VAIO 都係用128ssd+ 500hdd(己用90ssd+200hdd)呢個配搭，所以新電腦既128 其實唔太足夠長遠使用。<br />\n<br />\n所以我就睇下升級邊隻ssd會比較抵玩，暫時我會偏向選擇 Samsung m.2 850evo (500GB) 同埋 960evo nvme(256GB)。<br />\n<br />\n問題就尼啦，Nvme其實有無呢個必要，除左速度之外。始終850evo 係舊過960evo 兩年有多，早期3D Nand 技術上係唔係真係成熟? 睇跑分, 1800mb vs 500mb 兩者相差睇落好大。<br />\n<br />\n我睇過好多評測文，始終850既開箱文都係基於兩年前既市場/技術為準，兩年後既今日會唔會過時? 除左呢兩隻ssd之外，巴打門會唔會有其他好介紹?<br />\n<br />\nxps13:  sandisk x400 m.2 128gb <br />\n<br />\n用途: YouTube,  LOL,  BF3 , 輕量photoshop/lightroom <br />\n<br />\n目標:一換就用三，四年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/124604_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F124604_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=5ed28291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/124609_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F124609_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7018dfae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97253eda2c0470ac4297230439e0759343d5c3a1","tid":492951,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"Sm961"}]}